Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获龙之转矩 返回拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢 做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然转移时会增加负荷 但大概能行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有异时空物体急速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香…香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具在漂浮着？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊这个波动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不是不可预知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺因 为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在于宇宙中的垃圾们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把龙之转矩交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:02:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不允许你们玷污龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 去追龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多说了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚吧 你们不应该存在于这个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N 朋\N \N \N  \N友 \N \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往前 往前 就这样继续往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应变强了 就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继上山以后 这次是仓库么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里向右拐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 我还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有搞错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是遥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事吗 没受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是突然跑到车子前面很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有跑到车子前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 可不能和大人开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 该不会刚才撞到头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 小姐 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思 那我这就告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂最近的小孩在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为有把砖头吃掉的虫子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在出谜语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 所以我讨厌大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 再稍微调查一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砖墙上有一些小孔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是被雷射射到的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里来的闲人干的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异常者发现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟儿们已经归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速进行救治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我被盯上了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到该去私塾的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上乃木 你现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺路稍微去了下佑家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 阿姨不让我见他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机好像也被没收掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好的办法没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库拉拉 不能捡掉在地上的东西吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要吃青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是遥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么关系啊 那种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为他们用严肃的表情在谈论什么的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然笑起来对上目光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会受打击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据山田亚库尼斯的恋爱占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我调查了自己和班级里男生的相合度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我发现 我和藤原相性很合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便我也调查了遥和藤原之间的相性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥和藤原？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢 真是吓一跳 相性最高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥一定也看过那个占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且藤原和遥说话的时候 总是嬉皮笑脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把龙之转矩 消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是消灭 捕获才是我们的任务不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它才是造成这个时空不正常的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不消灭它的话 这整个宇宙 所有一切都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个拉库利玛已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩也不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 和我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 美保也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才勇去过遥的家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 藤原？你还真什么都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么他去干什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事有什么好说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫那种事啊 给我好好回答啊 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:10:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么吞吞吐吐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在于衔尾龙所指明的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存于这整个宇宙中的生物 都在渴求你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好听我说话么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有个奇怪的老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里有啊 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被盯上了 被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上的不是后藤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢 好像是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你快回答我藤原为什么要去遥你家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都说了是担心佑的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原去了佑的家 被阿姨赶出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也不让我和佑见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑就那样一直被关在房间里的话 会变的不正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以藤原担心佑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗 爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 为什么要生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥总有一天要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了恐吓你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是保护不了遥的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和我一起去的话 阿姨反而会更讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起去也不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如去和雪惠商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样阿姨更要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑已经够可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的阿姨可是很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时是束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想到什么好的方法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 刚才差点忘了 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爱一样的手机挂件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会带来好运的小鸡 海子还会再做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就给上乃木吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有短信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我去去就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上乃木？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再联络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 我也正好有话要对爱说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么今天藤原也会去遥家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是佑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个理由昨天已经听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天也是来商量要不要一起去佑的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 佑 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说都是后藤的关系咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你去问藤原好了 我来打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 爱也有从藤原那里拿到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己高兴就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装傻也要有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁装傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个朝三暮四的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌遥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原也最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 爱你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我妹妹海子做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你还需要什么护身符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原拿着反正最后会弄掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我拿着 这个挂件也会比较幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 不要弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 真是个讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经很久都没有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换的衣服放这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉前不要忘了刷牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 要是吵架了赶快去道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为….为什么你会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸上都写着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你先去道歉比较好哦 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使认为自己没有错 也要自己先去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和好的要领
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无聊的小事失去重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说去道歉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我有做了什么坏事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让爱生气的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是离你未来很近的之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂件 朋友 都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂件？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌遥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长古川 吃这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带零食到学校来是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然是想吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 把这个拿走 快快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 欺负人可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼 要折断了 折断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不松手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 对藤原…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的雨你到哪里去啊 遥 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才看到的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没有拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
